---
title: Creamy Mushroom, Rosemary & Bacon Fettuccine with Cucumber Salad & Parmesan
description: Meaty field mushrooms work a treat with aromatic rosemary, crispy bacon and a silky, Parmesan-spiked sauce in this crowd-pleasing pasta dish. Serve with a sweet and peppery salad to cut the richness and meet your new go-to pasta dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-mushroom-rosemary-fettuccine-8b47ddc3.jpg
